quran[20{c,v,t}:
44,40,Inna yawmal fasli meeqaatuhum ajma'een
44,41,Yawma laa yughnee mawlan 'am mawlan shai'anw wa laa hum yunsaroon
44,42,Illaa mar rahimal laah' innahoo huwal 'azeezur raheem
44,43,Inna shajarataz zaqqoom
44,44,Ta'aamul aseem
44,45,Kalmuhli yaghlee filbutoon
44,46,Kaghalyil hameem
44,47,Khuzoohu fa'tiloohu ilaa sawaaa'il laheem
44,48,Summa subboo fawqa raasihee min 'azaabil hameem
44,49,Zuq innaka antal 'azeezul kareem
44,50,Inna haazaa maa kuntum bihee tamtaroon
44,51,Innal muttaqeena fee maqaamin ameen
44,52,Fee jannaatinw wa 'uyoon
44,53,Yalbasoona min sundusinw wa istbraqim mutaqaabileen
44,54,Kazaalika wa zawwajnaahum bihoorin 'een
44,55,Yad'oona feehaa bikulli faakihatin aamineen
44,56,Laa yazooqoona feehal mawtaa illal mawtatal oolaa wa qaqaahum 'azaabal jaheem
44,57,Fadlam mir rabbik; zaalika huwal fawzul 'azeem
44,58,Fa innamaa yassarnaahu bilisaanika la'allahum yatazakkaroon
44,59,Fartaqib innahum murta qiboon
